pulltitle: Remove README rationale for repo being private
pullsbody:
I've read through this code and confirmed the only possible piece of data that's not public is the URL to the LDAP server. I've checked with jabba and confirmed that this URL is not private and it can be made public.

This PR removes the readme text explaining why the repo is private. I'll make the repo public after we merge it.
